msgctxt "57b6e608-7828-4f63-81c3-ddf467790ea5"
msgid ""
"Sometimes you can't use your <link=\"Encyclopedia:Dexterity\""
"><b>Dexterity</b></link> bonus (if you have one). If you can't react to a "
"blow, you can't use your Dexterity bonus to <link=\"Encyclopedia:"
