#. Mechanics/Blueprints/Encyclopedia/Lore_Religion_BlockText_Text
msgctxt "43e8c9a7-5e58-4aad-8e2b-417141621350"
msgid ""
"(<link=\"Encyclopedia:Intelligence\"><b>Intelligence</b></link>; Trained "
